{
  "texts": [
    "Unlike other consensus mechanisms, a block created with the PoW mechanism contains ''nonce'' data.",
    "A block created with the PoS mechanism contains the data ''validatorId'', ''validatorName'' and ''validatorStake''.",
    "A block created with the PoA mechanism contains the data ''validatorId'' and ''validatorPublicKey''.",
    "The block size of sensitive patient data is larger than that of non-sensitive patient data.",
    "The sensitive data are fragmented and encrypted in smaller sizes compared to the non-sensitive data."
  ]
}